<div class="container">
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2>Find Friends Who Didn't Complete Their 2014 Ballot</h2>
      <h2>And Aren't Being Counted</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p class="text-center">Hi!  This is a tool (quickly made) that searches your friend's names against the current Unsigned Ballot List in Oregon.  We're fighting for Measure 92.  None of your information will be shared in any way with any party.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-2">
          <span class="step">1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <p>Please press the login button, accept the permissions.</p>
            <p>Your information will not be used for another purpose or stored in any way.</p>
            <p>Made by Lawrence Whiteside.  Reach him&nbsp;
              <a href="mailto:law@cinemasetfree.com">here</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              The code for this project is open-sourced and available here:
              <a target="_blank" href='http://github.com/lawwantsin/unsignedFriends'>Source Code</a>
            </p> 
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="login">
            <div class="login2">
              <fb:login-button scope="public_profile,email,user_friends" onlogin="checkLoginState();">
              </fb:login-button>        
            </div>
          </div>  
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-2">
          <span class="step">2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-10">    
          <div class="friends">
            <div id="status"></div>  
            <p class="searching">Searching the Unsigned ballot database now... May take a minute.</p>
            <div class="found-none">
              <h2>We didn't find any matches amongst your friends.  Good stuff!</h2>
              <p>Now Share this so your friends can search their friends too.</p>          
            </div>
            <div  class="found-some">
              <h2>
                We found some matches!  
              </h2>
              <p>
                If they are Oregon voters, please message them ASAP.</p>
              <p>The deadline is <%= ((Date.today - Date.new(2014, 11, 18)).abs * 24).to_i %> hours away!</p>          
              <p>Help your friends get counted.  Measure 92 is on the line!</p>          
              <div class="row matched-list">
              
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-2">
          <span class="step">3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-10">
          <p>Share this page with your friends so they can check too.  Tell them how easy it was.</p>
          <div class="fb-like" data-share="true" data-width="450" data-show-faces="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
